                  <h3 style="font-weight:bold; display:inline;"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>SEC. 25.</i></font></h3> <font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Item 0840-001-0001 of Section 2.00 of the Budget Act of 2026 is amended to read:</i></font>
               </div>
               <div>
