                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>5.</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (2), $7,700,000 shall support Medi-Cal payment increases for Congregate Living Health
                           Facilities for dates of service prior to the transition of applicable services into the managed care delivery system.</i></font>
                        </td>
