                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>The Department of Health Care Services may require Medi-Cal providers, Medi-Cal managed care plans, and other persons or entities
                           pertaining to the Medi-Cal program to submit information the department
