                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">16.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Notwithstanding Chapter 1 (commencing with Section 18000) of Part 6 of Division 9 of the Welfare and Institutions Code, a
                           loan not to exceed $125,587,000 shall be made available from the General Fund, from funds not otherwise appropriated, to cover
                           the federal or reimbursable share, or both, of costs of a program or programs when the federal funds or reimbursements have
