                        <td valign="top" width="24">1.</td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(a)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">
                           <div style="">Funds appropriated in this item shall not be encumbered unless every rule or regulation adopted and every all-county letter
