                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">5.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Notwithstanding any other law, upon approval of the Department of Finance, expenditure authority may be transferred
                              					 between schedules within or between the following items for the State Department of Education and the State Department
                              of Social Services: Items 6100-201-0890 and 5180-101-0890, and reimbursements. The aggregate amount of appropriation increases
                              provided under this section during the fiscal year may not exceed the aggregate amount of appropriation decreases. This provision
                              supports the continuity of care in the programs transitioned from the State Department of Education to the State Department
                              of Social Services.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
