                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Upon notification by the Department of Social Services, the Controller is authorized to transfer funds from this item to the
                              CalFresh E&amp;T Workers’ Compensation Fund in accordance with Section 18926.8 of the Welfare and Institutions Code. This provision
                              also applies to Item 5180-141-0890 of the Budget Act of 2023 (Chs. 12, 38, and 189, Stats. 2023) and Item 5180-141-0890 of
