                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><style>span.DottedLeaders::after {content:"..................";}</style><font color="#B30000"><s>Of the funds appropriated in this item, $5,000,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for the Black Immigrant and Refugee
                           Equity Project.
                           			 These funds shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure until June 30, 2028.</s></font>
                        </td>
