                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>23.</i></font></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>(a)</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the funds appropriated in this item, $12,000,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for outreach, coordination, and
                           services under the Enhanced Services for Asylees and Vulnerable Noncitizens Program as established in Section 13650 of the
                           Welfare and Institutions Code, and shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure until June 30, 2029.</i></font>
                        </td>
