                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>33.</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the funds appropriated in this item, $4,000,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for Feeding San Diego.</i></font></td>
