                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the funds appropriated in this item, $1,500,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for Every Day Action for infrastructure,
                           vehicles, and operations.</i></font>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
