                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">1.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">In accordance with federal law, the funds appropriated in Schedule (1) shall be distributed to local and state agencies on
