                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(3)</td>
                        <td colspan="3" valign="top" width="241">The total balance of carryover funds at the beginning of each fiscal year, and how much carryover funds are currently available.</td>
