                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">44.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $3,000,000 shall be available on a one-time basis for the University of California,
                           Los Angeles Ralph J. Bunche Center for African American Studies to support research, training, and community-engaged programs
                           on the condition of Black life in California.
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
