                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><style>span.DottedLeaders::after {content:"..................";}</style><font color="#B30000"><s>Funds
                           			 appropriated in Provisions 34, 36, 37, 38, 39, 40, 41, 42, 43, and 44 of this item shall be available for encumbrance
                           or expenditure without regard to fiscal years.</s></font>
                        </td>
