                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of
                           					 the amount appropriated in this item, $5,260,000 shall be available on a one-time basis to the University of California,
                           Berkeley for Cal Stadium Lighting.</i></font>
                        </td>
