                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>51.</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the amount appropriated in this item, $200,000 shall be available on a one-time basis to the University of California,
