                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>53.</i></font></td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Of the amount appropriated in this item, $15,000,000 shall be available on a one-time basis to the University of California
                           for UC Journalism Fellowships.</i></font>
                        </td>
