                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(2)</td>
                        <td colspan="3" valign="top" width="240">
                           <div style="">Pursuant to Section 79149.3 of the Education Code, the reimbursement rate shall be $10.61 per hour.</div>
