                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(c)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (2), $14,337,000 shall be available to support the California Healthy School Food Pathways
                           program. Funds appropriated pursuant to this subprovision shall be available for encumbrance
                           					 or expenditure until June 30,<style>span.DottedLeaders::after {content:"..................";}</style><font color="#B30000"><s> 2029</s></font><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i> 2029. Of these funds, at least 80 percent shall support direct program costs, including instruction and training for participants.</i></font>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
