            <div id="s1470.13690629423738987">
               <div style="margin:0 0 1em 0" class="ActionLine">
                  <h3 style="font-weight:bold; display:inline;"><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>SEC. 147.</i></font></h3> <font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i>Item 6870-488 of Section 2.00 of the Budget Act of 2026 is amended to read:</i></font>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <table frame="">
                     <tr>
                        <td colspan="7" valign="top" width="336">
                           <div style="">6870-488—Reappropriation (Proposition 98), Board of Governors of the California Community Colleges. Notwithstanding any other law,
                              the balances from the following appropriations are available for reappropriation for the purposes specified in Provision 1:
