                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">3.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Funding provided in Schedule (1)(c) of this item is limited to the purposes described in Provision 4 of this item.</td>
